{"about_the_game":"Luminis: Heal Them All is a small-scale open world survival shooter set in a futuristic world. In this game, your task is to explore, survive and heal every sick being you see using a variety of healing devices that resemble firearms. You cannot kill in this game, so it's not for the bloodthirsty.<br><br><strong>Heal the Sick</strong><br>A strange virus has found its way in your world. It is not only able to modify the DNA sequence of the animals, but can also infect AI software installed in robots, changing their behavior. As a volunteer who left everything behind to pursue an adventure, you are sent into an expedition to investigate what's going on.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2548670/extras/HealingShowcaseV3.gif?t=1710143735\" /><br><br><strong>Thrilling 'Combat'</strong><br>Yes. You heal aggressive animals and robots by shooting them with healing 'weapons'. Once you manage to heal them, they stop attacking you and may even thank you with some gifts. There are a variety of therapeutic rifles, pistols, shotguns and snipers that can be found in the world. Find them, and they will prove to be excellent companions in times of crisis.<br><br><strong>Explore</strong><br>Roam around the wild and find useful loot. In Luminis, there are resources such as food, equipment, medical items, crafting materials that are scattered across the world. Use them to your advantage.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2548670/extras/Loot_Optimized.gif?t=1710143735\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2548670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1710143735","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2548670/page.bg.jpg?t=1710143735","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2548670/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=171014